mmgpy.metamodel¶

The metamodel module provides the surrogate models available for the metamodelling process. Currently supported regression models are the following.

General regression models¶

  • Random Forest Regression (RFR) metamodel.RandomForestRegression()

  • Support Vector Regression (SVR) metamodel.SupportVectorRegression()

  • Feed Forward Neural Network Regression (FFNNR) metamodel.FeedForwardNNRegression()

Series regression models¶

  • Convolutional Neural Network Series Regression (CNNSR)
